OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781172387
OL,3,CWorshippers locked in mosque as people
OL,4,Cattacked in Glasgow unrest
OL,6,FA 30-year-old Sudanese man, Hadi
OL,7,FAlodid, has appeared in court charged
OL,8,Fwith the attack, with the 44-year-old
OL,9,Fvictim, Stephen Ogilvie, said to have
OL,10,Flost an eye as a result.
OL,12,FProtesters took to the streets in
OL,13,Fseveral parts of Scotland, including
OL,14,FGlasgow city centre. Some of those
OL,15,Finvolved referenced the murder of 18-
OL,16,Fyear-old Henry Nowak, with one banner
OL,17,Fsaying "white lives matter".
OL,26,@yD@HOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
