OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781172387
OL,3,CWorshippers locked in mosque as people
OL,4,Cattacked in Glasgow unrest
OL,6,FVideos circulating on social media
OL,7,Fappear to show violent clashes between
OL,8,Fthose taking part in the protest in
OL,9,FGlasgow and members of the public.
OL,11,FPolice Scotland's Assistant Chief
OL,12,FConstable Alan Waddell said: "We
OL,13,Funderstand the concerns people have
OL,14,Fabout their communities and will
OL,15,Falways balance the right to freedom of
OL,16,Fexpression with the need to tackle
OL,17,Fcrime without fear or favour."
OL,26,@tD@^OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
