PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781172387
OL,3,CWorshippers locked in mosque as people
OL,4,Cattacked in Glasgow unrest
OL,6,F"I would strongly condemn that
OL,7,Foffending and send a clear message
OL,8,Fthat there is no place for racism and
OL,9,Fviolence in Scotland," he said.
OL,11,FScottish Labour leader Anas Sarwar
OL,12,Fsaid worshippers in Glasgow Central
OL,13,FMosque had to be locked in the
OL,14,Fbuilding, as marchers appeared to be
OL,15,Fheading towards it.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
